{
  "$schema": "./schema/registry.schema.json",
  "description": "Hand-curated registry of ippoan frontend dev servers. Source of truth for name -> port assignments. Each entry reserves a port for the listed repo; the repo's .ippoan-dev.yaml must mirror its entry (enforced by ci/Dev Proxy Validate). Add/remove via PR against this file.",
